    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1game_1_1System" kindref="compound">System</ref> that processes 2D movement and rotation for entities. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This system reads from Move2DComponent and applies physics simulation including rotation towards target angle, velocity integration, and dampening when input is inactive.</para>
<para>The system updates TransformComponent with the computed rotation and translation changes each frame.</para>
<para>Required components:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Move2DComponent (physics configuration and state)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>TransformComponent (receives transform updates) </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
